Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:58.20,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,真是漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:01.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,能夠如此輕易地躲開這利樁的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這個世界上恐怕也就只有你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:06.42,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,紅方的Lancer啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:13.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,原來如此 你正是適合阻擋在此地之王面前的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不敢當 異國的王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:18.70,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,然後我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:23.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,對你來說 這利刺既是攻擊 又是防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:25.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,既是示威 也是恐怖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:30.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,穩定領地 穩定居城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.67,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,穩定應當守護的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:37.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,也就是說 你想要僅憑自己形成一個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這是靠對祖國的愛完成的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:45.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,還是出自身為王的責任感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:49.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,是想揭露余的內心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:51.32,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是異國的王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.20,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這裡並沒有你的麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.60,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,王也許是孤高的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:05:02.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是也不存在沒有麾下單獨上戰場的王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:06.52,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,然後 我是英靈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,即便與一國為敵也無所畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:12.97,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:16.27,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,獨自與這國家為敵也無所畏懼嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:19.67,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不愧是英雄！ 不愧是余的敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:23.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 你早已在余的死亡陷阱之內！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:36.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,很遺憾 余的寶具的本質並非「利樁」…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,刺出的利樁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.97,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這一概念本身就是寶具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:44.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:49.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,只要你還在余的領域之內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,就無法逃離這個寶具！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:57.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,來吧 結束這一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:01.00,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,紅方的Lancer！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:13.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,火焰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,有趣…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,哈哈哈哈哈哈哈這就是叛逆！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:52.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,叛逆就是我的一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:01.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:05.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,很好 再多來一些…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:09.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,再對來一些！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:14.60,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:18.70,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,他叛逆的精神化作實體的姿態！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:22.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,吾輩的大綱並沒出錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:28.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,還真有如此恐怖的寶具啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:28.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,沒錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那正是「疵獸的咆吼」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,{\fs31\pos(696,600)}Crying Warmonger
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:34.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,能夠將受到的傷害變換為魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,並化作自己的力量的寶具！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,斯巴達克斯既是劍鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:44.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,也是為被虐待的人們挺身而出的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,他的生存方式在成為從者後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:50.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,便被升華成為了那寶具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.77,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 雖說能將傷痛化作力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:56.37,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,也並非無窮無盡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:57.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,正是如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,極限已經近在眼前了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:05.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那位大英雄馬上就會放出一生最強的一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.70,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,然後消失了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.70,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,接著那正是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:16.97,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我們御主的革命劇的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.57,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我的鐵拳即是愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,來吧！ 接受我的愛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:28.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,休想逃走！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:30.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:50.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,在那裡嗎 壓政者！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:53.27,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什麼…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:57.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那個方向是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:08.60,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,真是煩人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:11.52,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你這樣的戰鬥方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,已經是對騎士王的侮辱了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:20.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,齊格！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,已經到極限了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:30.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,齊格！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:33.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你的身體…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,雖然不懂怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不過已經要結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,反正說到底不過是贗品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:40.60,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,是不可能敵得過我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:46.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,紅方的Berserker？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:50.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,壓政者啊 在我的愛中毀滅吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:57.77,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你這 骯髒的肉球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:08.32,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,少開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,Saber 快點撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:12.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,立刻離開那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:15.17,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那傢伙非常不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:23.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:27.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,好… 好噁心…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:30.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不要動 傷口很深
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那邊的兩位 請快逃跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這裡很危險 快一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你是… 為什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:39.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.77,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,明明這條命是妳救回來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:46.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 我覺得 無論如何都得這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:48.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.27,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不要責怪他！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:55.12,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,他是為了保護身臨險境的我而戰鬥的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,然後才會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:01.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,必須快點離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:07.00,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不 我已經動不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你才應該快點離開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:13.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你不是應該在這裡毀滅的從者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:15.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那麼 起碼黑方的Ri…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:15.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:16.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.12,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不要不要不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你也不是小孩子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:23.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我說不要就是不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:25.57,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我也不能逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:27.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,如果Ruler是我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:29.67,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,也不會把他丟在這裡逃走吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:35.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,唉 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.47,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你都這麼說了也就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:42.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我也有不能逃離這裡的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:49.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,請不要離開這裡 絕對！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.37,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:11:59.32,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,斯巴達克斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.45,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我不能讓你這樣的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,傷害無辜的民眾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,時機已到…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:16.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我的一擊將破壞所有的壓制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:19.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,粉碎所有的權力！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:22.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這就是斯巴達克斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:28.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我的旗幟啊 請守護我的同胞吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,吾的神明在此！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,{\fs31}Luminosite Eternlle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:18.71,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,啊 還活著 得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:21.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,好痛… 請讓開一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:22.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:27.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,各位都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:28.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.97,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,死在這裡吧 Lancer！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,大地啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,太慢了！ 天空啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:13.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,牆壁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:24.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,寶具嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:26.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,梵天啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:26.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,{\fs31}Brahma
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:34.45,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,御主正在召集我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:37.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,下次再決一勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:39.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什麼？ 你！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:47.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,達尼克嗎… 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:53.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:14:59.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:02.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:11.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,難道…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:47.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,真沒想到居然還有這樣的手段…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:55.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,現在 長久以來一直守護的尤格多米雷尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:58.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,被逼入了絕境… 這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:02.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:06.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 這種程度的苦境
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:09.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,在這百年來 已經有過無數次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:14.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,八十年前 尤格多米雷尼亞得到衰落的預言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:17.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,無法再次作為魔術師出人頭地的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我參加了冬木的聖杯戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:23.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,利用了國家與軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:26.32,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,有時甚至連協助者都被我當成棄子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:28.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,為了延長壽命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.00,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不斷吞噬他人的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,現在就連我自己都不知道自己是誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,即便如此 我也要得到大聖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:41.12,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,怎麼可能又會將其交給別人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:44.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,難以置信…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:46.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:48.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,大聖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:50.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,如果是從者就能明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:56.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那就是我們所彼此爭奪的大聖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,看來我必須得去一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:07.12,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這將是質問紅方的最後機會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:12.57,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,之後我會好好說教齊格你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:16.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我明白了 我會做好心理準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:34.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,看來這邊還沒有探知術式的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:36.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:45.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,看來 來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:47.12,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:18:00.20,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,省得余去找你了 紅方的Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:03.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,剛才失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:08.42,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,就在這裡重新戰鬥 來對你盡到禮數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:11.45,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你要由我來打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:15.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,這次餘一定會將你刺成串的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.45,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,怎麼了？ 黑方的Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:05.52,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,跟剛才不一樣 動作裡缺乏精彩之處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.57,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,孤高的王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:11.17,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,在救援到來之前要休息嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:14.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,即便與多人作戰我也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:23.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什麼…？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:37.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:40.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,余的力量在這難道行不通嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:45.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,還是魔力的供給被抑制了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:48.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是紅方的Lancer啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:53.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,余即便賭上龍公之名也要擊敗你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:00.67,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那裡是紅方的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:07.37,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,無法完全發揮身為王的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:09.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,是贏不了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:13.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,達尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:14.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你知道關於余的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:21.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不遜又令人極為不快的傳說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:24.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:27.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,後世之人總是對死者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:30.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,擅自抱有幻想…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,沒錯 總是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:38.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 余絕對無法原諒！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,玷汙余之一族的名聲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:45.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,將餘光榮的生存方式籠罩上陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:49.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,即便是後世 也永遠應當被定罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:51.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,正是如此 王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:55.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,延續家名是我們的榮耀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:21:01.00,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,決不能允許被卑劣之人擅自傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:04.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,賭上瓦拉幾亞大公的名譽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:07.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,必須防止進一步的恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:10.42,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,因此余要託付給聖杯的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:14.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那就是將那口口相傳的骯髒的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:17.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,從余的歷史中抹消…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:19.37,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,遵命…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:22.45,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,所以必須要贏得這場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是達尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:27.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,雖然你也應該明白 但還是要多加提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:31.47,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,絕對不要讓余使用「那個」寶具…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:34.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,哪怕要難看地敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,余也絕對不會使用「那個」寶具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:42.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,若是你使用令咒強迫余的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:46.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,之後的事 就不必我多說了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:50.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,明白了「吾王」…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:55.37,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 既然如此就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.32,0:21:59.32,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,應當守護的是尤格多米雷尼亞的存續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:02.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,應當到達的是「根源的漩渦」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:06.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,無論如何都需要大聖杯…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:08.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,抱歉了Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.35,0:22:11.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我要打出王牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:15.85,Default-CN,,0,0,0,,第11話 永遠的光輝
